vfdata-courier-extra for Debian
-------------------------------

This is a Debianized version of courier-extra, a set of virtual font files
to use Courier extra weights and variants in LaTeX.

Installation
------------

Install the package, if you haven't yet.

  $ sudo dpkg -i vfdata-courier-extra*.deb

Configuration
-------------

  $ sudo mktexlsr

Testing
-------

  $ cp /usr/share/doc/vfdata-courier-extra/examples/courier-extra-test.tex ./
  $ latex courier-extra-test.tex
  $ dvipdfmx -f courier-extra.map courier-extra-test.dvi
  $ xpdf courier-extra-test.pdf &
  $ rm courier-extra-test.{tex,aux,log,dvi,pdf}
